gnu-ld - Assume the C compiler uses GNU ld
largefile - Support for 64-bit file offsets (http://www.unix.org/version2/whatsnew/lfs20mar.html)
man - Build and install manual pages
rindeal-config - Install sane default config files prepared by rindeal
rpath - Hardcode runtime library paths
static-libs - Build/use static libraries, do not arbitrarily flip!
shared-libs - Build/use shared dynamic libraries, do not arbitrarily flip!
system-jre - Use system-wide Java Runtime Environment instead of the bundled copy
